## Loading

```python
from datasets import load_dataset

# All rows, all languages
ds = load_dataset("PATH/TO/REPO", split="train")

# English only
en = ds.filter(lambda r: r["language"] == "en")

# Active under the prohibitions tranche (2 Feb 2025)
prohibitions = ds.filter(
    lambda r: r["chunk_type"] == "paragraph"
    and r["article_no"] in {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}
)
```

