## Limitations

- This snapshot reflects the OJ text **as it was when the Cellar bundle
  was generated**. The Commission may issue corrigenda; the EUR-Lex
  consolidated view at `source_url` is always authoritative.
- Footnotes (`<NOTE>` elements in Formex) are stripped: they describe
  legal sourcing rather than normative content. If you need them, parse
  the upstream Formex XML directly.
- LLM-assisted enrichment (risk_category, actor_roles, obligation_type)
  is **not** included in v1 — it's regex-only. Hand-curation + LLM
  classification is planned for a v2.

